### 1. 新增用药医嘱
POST http://localhost:8081/medicineOrder/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZXhwIjoxNzgzMDQzNTE1fQ.TlH6YPRU8hDfrPMAmolFuvB2cr9z8YkO1vZ36bacBqo

{
  "patientId": 2,
  "medicineName": "硝苯地平缓释片",
  "dosage": "20mg",
  "frequency": "每日两次",
  "remark": "饭后温水服用"
}

### 2. 修改医嘱
POST http://localhost:8081/medicineOrder/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZXhwIjoxNzgzMDQzNTE1fQ.TlH6YPRU8hDfrPMAmolFuvB2cr9z8YkO1vZ36bacBqo

{
  "id": 1,
  "patientId": 2,
  "medicineName": "硝苯地平控释片"
}

### 3. 删除单条医嘱
DELETE http://localhost:8081/medicineOrder/1
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 4. 查询单条医嘱详情
GET http://localhost:8081/medicineOrder/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZXhwIjoxNzgzMDQzNTE1fQ.TlH6YPRU8hDfrPMAmolFuvB2cr9z8YkO1vZ36bacBqo

### 5. 患者医嘱分页
GET http://localhost:8081/medicineOrder/page?patientId=2&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZXhwIjoxNzgzMDQzNTE1fQ.TlH6YPRU8hDfrPMAmolFuvB2cr9z8YkO1vZ36bacBqo

